hopobject.body: I don't like pubs infant ibuprofen 6 months Levi Johnston posed for Playgirl, but he didn't go the Full Monty. Bristol Palin's hunky baby daddy may not have shown everything, but his naked cover says enough. Inside the mag, Johnston's spread includes a tribute to "hockey moms" that features Johnston posing with a hockey stick. 'People are going to see more of Levi than they thought,' his manager Tank Jones told Usmagazine.com. 'He's ready to shock the world. The hell with 15 minutes.'
